{"word":"ἐναντίον","slug":"ἐναντίον","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b><el>ἐναντίον</el></b> [<a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ nt.\">nt.</a> of <el><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:ἐναντίος\">ἐναντίος</a></el>]<b><p class=\"pp1\"/>—<pp>1.</pp></b> functions as <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ adv.\">adv.</a> <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ w.\">w.</a> <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ art.\">art.</a> <el><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:τοὐναντίον\">τοὐναντίον</a></el> (<el>τὸ <a class=\"S\" href=\"S:ἐναντίον\">ἐναντίον</a></el>) <b>on the contrary <a href='B:540 2:7'>2 Cor 2:7</a>; <a href='B:550 2:7'>Gal 2:7</a>; <a href='B:670 3:9'>1 Pt 3:9</a>.<p class=\"pp1\"/>—<pp>2.</pp></b> functions as a <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ prep.\">prep.</a> <b><p class=\"pp3\"/>—<pp>a.</pp> in front of, before <a href='B:480 2:12'>Mk 2:12</a> <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ v.l.\">v.l.</a>; <a href='B:490 20:26'>Lk 20:26</a>; <a href='B:510 8:32'>Ac 8:32</a>.<p class=\"pp3\"/>—<pp>b.</pp></b> in extended sense of being subject to scrutiny <b>in the sight of <a href='B:490 1:6'>Lk 1:6</a>; <a href='B:490 24:19'>24:19</a>; <a href='B:510 7:10'>Ac 7:10</a>.</b> <center id=\"nav_bottom\"> <a id=\"left_arrow\" href=\"S:ἐναντιόομαι\">&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;</a> <a id=\"bottom_home\" href=\"S:#1.Table of Contents\">&emsp;&emsp;</a> <a id=\"right_arrow\" href=\"S:ἐναντίος\">&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;</a> </center> "}]}